08/08/2010
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Police have seized 135kg of marijuana and detained three suspected smugglers, interior ministry spokesperson Ivo Kotevski announced on Saturday (August 7th). The stash, worth 500,000 euros, was found in a pickup truck on the Veles-Negotino Highway. According to the police, the drugs were destined for the Swiss market. (Makfax, A1, Kanal 5, Sitel, MIA - 07/08/10)
